metadata.name: Paperfriends for Paperhands #1
metadata.description: Paperfriends are membership tokens to a private club of NFT curation. With each NFT you will have access to a private discord channel where NFT related strategies, intel, drop curation, whitelists are happenning in an isolated environment, far from the noise. Together with respected members of the NFT community, our team is trying to show ways and considerations accross the weekly NFT drops on various chains.
